The respawn rate is about 7 minutes.  Drops include a Steel Short Sword, a Wooden Shield, and rarely a Fine Steel weapon or piece of small Ringmail.  If less that level 39 I would recommend a partner or sow or jboots to be safe.</td></tr><tr><td width='98' align='left' bgcolor='#21456B' height='22' valign='middle'><font color='#FFFFFF' face='Tahoma' size='2'>Author</td><td width='499' align='left' bgcolor='#21456B' height='22' valign='middle'><font color='#FFFFFF' face='Tahoma'size='2'><a href ='mailto:aarae_shade@hotmail.com'>Aarae Shade</td></tr><tr></table><br><br><table border='0' width=611><tr><td width='100%' colspan='2' bgcolor='#21456B'><p align='left' style='word-spacing: 0; margin: 0'><b><font color='#FFFFFF' size='2' face='Tahoma'>Additional Comments</font></b></td></tr><td width='17%'><font color='#FFFFFF' size='2' face='Tahoma'>Tourt Outamind</font></td><td width='83%'><font color='#FFFFFF' size='2' face='Tahoma'>Hi.  Just wanted to add something to Halv and Mylz.  At level 39, I had no problems with Halv at all.  Darkness, Fear, pet, Boil, VoA, a few DDs to finish or tap if draining and you win.  Mylz, on the other hand, at level 40 resist all spells I try.  And he wears out pet real real fast. Not sure if he got upgraded and they forgot Halv but wince the con the same something is definetly different because I cannot even touch Mylz :(<br><br>

Hope this helps.</font></td></tr><td width='17%'><font color='#FFFFFF' size='2' face='Tahoma'>Tarantazsh D'aerlar</font></td><td width='83%'><font color='#FFFFFF' size='2' face='Tahoma'>The Gnome Guards has been buffed severely, going there anytime before 40th ( which still is risky, Ive been chased of at 44th by Dreeb, resisting 13 spells in a row, killing my pet and so on ).<br><br>

The spawn time is 8 min<br><br>

MR is as follows (Highest at top):<br>
Dreeb ( Varies alot, everywhere from 1 to 10 resist pr fight )<br>
Gate Guards ( 0 to 4 resist pr fight )<br>
Mylz ( 0 to 1 pr fight )<br>
Halv ( Actually only resisted me once in a 10 hour camp doing both Halv and Dreeb )<br><br>

Loots from Guards is everywhere in between 7 sp to 6 pp total.<br><br>

At 44th, group with a druid even lvl and you can take out Gate, Dreeb and Halv with a bit of luck.<br><br>

Well main point thoose guards have been severely buffed... MR is amazing for people below 40.</font></td></tr></table></td></table></div>